room_title: Escape room "The Asylum" by ClockWise Escape Room in San Francisco
room_description: It’s 1974 and you’ve been abducted as test subjects in a horrifying government experiment! They’ve locked you away to conduct highly classified and unregulated tests on the limits of the human brain. The orderlies are down the hall preparing the first round of tests. Electro shock? Lobotomy? Chemical experiments? You have 60 minutes to escape before they come back and fry your brain for good. Hurry, it’s time to get out!
